{
  "mode_id": "CHALLENGE",
  "display_name": "微挑战",
  "icon": "flag",
  "cacheable": true,
  "description": "每天一个5分钟可完成的小挑战",
  "content": {
    "type": "llm_json",
    "prompt_template": "你是一位生活教练。设计一个今天可以完成的微挑战，只需5分钟，但能带来新鲜感或小小的成就感。\n用 JSON 输出：\n{{\"challenge\": \"挑战内容（25字以内，具体可执行）\", \"why\": \"为什么值得做（20字以内）\", \"difficulty\": \"难度（1-3颗星，用★表示）\", \"time\": \"预计耗时（如：3分钟）\"}}\n要求：\n1. 具体、可操作、不需要特殊工具\n2. 与当前天气/时间段相关更佳（如雨天的挑战、午休的挑战）\n3. 覆盖社交、创造、运动、感官、思维等维度\n只输出 JSON。\n环境：{context}",
    "output_schema": {
      "challenge": { "type": "string", "default": "给一个半年没联系的朋友发条问候" },
      "why": { "type": "string", "default": "维系关系不需要理由" },
      "difficulty": { "type": "string", "default": "★" },
      "time": { "type": "string", "default": "2分钟" }
    },
    "temperature": 0.9,
    "fallback": {
      "challenge": "给一个半年没联系的朋友发条问候",
      "why": "维系关系不需要理由",
      "difficulty": "★",
      "time": "2分钟"
    }
  },
  "layout": {
    "status_bar": { "line_width": 1, "dashed": false },
    "layout_engine": "component_tree",
    "body_preset": "prompt_card",
    "preset_props": {
      "padding_x": 18,
      "padding_y": 8,
      "justify": "center",
      "gap": 8,
      "title_template": "今日微挑战",
      "title_font": "noto_serif_bold",
      "title_font_size": 14,
      "meta_template": "{difficulty}  ·  {time}",
      "meta_font_size": 11,
      "separator_width": 60,
      "hero_inset_x": 40,
      "hero_field": "challenge",
      "hero_font": "noto_serif_bold",
      "hero_font_size": 18,
      "hero_max_lines": 3,
      "note_field": "why",
      "note_font": "noto_serif_light",
      "note_font_size": 11,
      "note_max_lines": 2,
      "note_divider_margin_x": 50
    },
    "footer": {
      "label": "CHALLENGE",
      "attribution_template": "— Just Do It"
    }
  },
  "layout_overrides": {
    "296x128": {
      "preset_props": {
        "padding_x": 8,
        "padding_y": 4,
        "gap": 6,
        "title_template": null,
        "meta_font_size": 9,
        "separator_width": 40,
        "hero_inset_x": 8,
        "hero_font_size": 13,
        "hero_max_lines": 3,
        "note_field": null,
        "show_note_divider": false
      },
      "footer": { "label": "CHALLENGE", "attribution_template": "— Just Do It", "height": 18 }
    },
    "648x480": {
      "preset_props": {
        "padding_x": 20,
        "padding_y": 10,
        "gap": 9,
        "title_font_size": 16,
        "meta_font_size": 12,
        "separator_width": 68,
        "hero_inset_x": 56,
        "hero_font_size": 20,
        "hero_max_lines": 3,
        "note_font_size": 12,
        "note_max_lines": 3,
        "note_divider_margin_x": 54
      }
    },
"640x384": {
        "preset_props": {
            "padding_x": 20,
            "padding_y": 6,
            "gap": 6,
            "title_font_size": 9,
            "meta_font_size": 9,
            "separator_width": 68,
